{"word":"H4334 - מִישֹׁור - mîyshôwr - mee-shore' - Equity","slug":"H4334","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">מִישֹׁור</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>mîyshôwr"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>mee-shore'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Equity"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05DE;&#x05D9;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05E8;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05DE;&#x05D9;&#x05E9;&#x05C1;&#x05D5;&#x05E8; - m&#x0131;&#x0302;ysho&#x0302;r  m&#x0131;&#x0302;ysho&#x0302;r</b> - <i>mee-shore', mee-shore'</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H3474\">H3474</a>; a <i>level</i>, that is, a <i>plain</i> (often used (with the article prefixed) as a proper name of certain districts); figuratively <i>concord</i>; also <i>straightness</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>justice</i> (sometimes adverbially <i>justly</i>): - equity, even place, plain, right (-eously), (made) straight, uprightness."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H3474\">H3474</a>, <a href=\"#/H3475\">H3475</a>, <a href=\"#/H3476\">H3476</a>, <a href=\"#/H3477\">H3477</a>, <a href=\"#/H3483\">H3483</a>, <a href=\"#/H3484\">H3484</a>, <a href=\"#/H4339\">H4339</a>, <a href=\"#/H8289\">H8289</a>, <a href=\"#/H8290\">H8290</a>"}]}